Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:05.74,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}放开手脚大闹一场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.28,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Life’s just a tightrope, why not stop to fool around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}人生就是一场走钢丝  为何不停下享乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.58,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}"Chaotic good" is peak right now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.58,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}混乱已至巅峰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:13.54,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}I can show ya how
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:13.54,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}我会带你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.75,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Don’t get confused, we are not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.75,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}别误会了  我们不是一路人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.50,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}I’m a ruthless dame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.50,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}我可是个悍妇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:25.47,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}"Good vs Evil" is so overdone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:25.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}正义对决邪恶有点夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.22,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Let’s all kick back and party
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.22,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}让我们一脚踹开是非开趴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.47,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Just leave it to moi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}全交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.56,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Loosen my lips
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.56,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}玩我的嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.01,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Loosen my li-li-lips
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.01,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}玩我的嘴巴吧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:34.73,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}That’s karma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:34.73,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}这是报应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.19,0:23:38.94,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Loosen my lips
